    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SEATTLE/TACOMA\nSAU LAKE CITY\nRENO\nTON/ BALTIMORC\nOS ANGELES\nTULSAI\nOKLAHOMA CITY\nSAN DIEGO •\nALBUQUERQUE AMARILLO\nTUCSON\nHOUSTON •\nFORENNERS\nCOUPALM OCACH\n•ORT LAUDERDALE\nMIAME\nLONDON\nFRANKFURT\n• MILAN\nMADRID\nLISBON\nBARCELONA\nTEL AVIV\nCAIRO\nTRANS WORLD ROUTES\nTWAH",
      "TWA\nTIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE DEC. 13, 1980-JAN. 7, 1981\nTWA's Airport Express'®\nThe fast lane\nto the airplane.\nWith TWA's Round Trip\nYou go straight to the\nCheck-In, coming back\ngate. That's it.\nis simple.\nTWA takes care of you,\nso you can take care of business."
